Class CilBuilder

    • com.peyrona.mingle.cil.CilBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.peyrona.mingle.lang.interfaces.ICmdEncDecLib
    public class CilBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.peyrona.mingle.lang.interfaces.ICmdEncDecLib
    Serializes and deserializes instances of ICommand.

    As Mingle transpiler writes to JSON, this implementation uses same JSON format to store the IComands.
    This is more natural and makes easier writing the unbuild(...) because it just invokes the Serializer class (which is used by the transpiler to serialize the ICommand standard representations).
